<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>491</hymn_number>
<title>SUNGLAWI NGAI IN A RA CH491</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa a ra, sunglawi ngaiin, Ho-sa-na tiin phun kip an au, Maw nunnem
 Khamhtu na lam ah, Tum-hnah le puan kha an phah hna.

[C1]
   Bawipa a ra sunglawi ngaiin, Lungnem te-in thih awk caah .

[V2]
 Bawipa a ra, sunglawi ngaiin, Van ralkap hna nih van in an cuanh, A
 thih lai kha an hngalh caah, Ngaihchiat buin an run cuanh ko.

[C2]
   Bawipa a ra sunglawi ngaiin, Lungnem te-in thih awk caah .

[V3]
 Bawipa a ra, sunglawi ngaiin, Harnak caan tihnung a nai ko cang, Pa
 nih van sui thutdan cungin, Fapa ngeihchun cu a run zoh.

[C3]
   Bawipa a ra sunglawi ngaiin, Lungnem te-in thih awk caah .

[V4]
 Bawipa a ra, Sunglawi ngaiin, Lung nem tein thih awk caah, Lungfak
 tein nan lukhun u, Pathian sunparnak a langh hlan.

[C4]
   Bawipa a ra sunglawi ngaiin, Lungnem te-in thih awk caah .</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
</song>